nodes.text: Skywalker Ranch was a destination on Coruscant's subtram in the Coruscant underworld.

The name was inserted onto the subtram map as an in-joke by the production team, along with the other destinations on the map, referencing the real-world Skywalker Ranch, which was the main production studio for Lucasfilm. The stop in question is the middle bottom stop on the map, marked in green, where "Skywalker Ranch" is written out in Aurebesh.
